toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-thu-vien-cho-thu-vien-tieu-hoc\/#giai_phap_oliver_v5_hien_dai_than_thien_va_hieu_qua\" >Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p Oliver v5 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-thu-vien-cho-thu-vien-tieu-hoc\/#vi_sao_thu_vien_tieu_hoc_can_phan_mem_quan_ly_chuyen_nghiep\" >V\u00ec sao th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-thu-vien-cho-thu-vien-tieu-hoc\/#oliver_%e2%80%93_phan_mem_quan_ly_thu_vien_thong_minh\" >Oliver \u2013 Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng minh<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-thu-vien-cho-thu-vien-tieu-hoc\/#tinh_nang_noi_bat_cua_oliver\" >T\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Oliver<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-thu-vien-cho-thu-vien-tieu-hoc\/#loi_ich_cua_oliver_doi_voi_thu_vien_tieu_hoc\" >L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a Oliver \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"giai_phap_oliver_v5_hien_dai_than_thien_va_hieu_qua\"><\/span>Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p Oliver v5 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1, th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i l\u01b0u gi\u1eef s\u00e1ch m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u01a1i g\u1ee3i ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea \u0111\u1ecdc v\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 tri th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1ea1o tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch v\u0103n h\u00f3a \u0111\u1ecdc, ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n cho th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-16594\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/2258780.webp\" alt=\"PH\u1ea6N M\u1ec0M TH\u01af VI\u1ec6N CHO TH\u01af VI\u1ec6N TI\u1ec2U H\u1eccC\n\" width=\"900\" height=\"493\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/2258780.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/2258780-730x400.webp 730w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/2258780-768x421.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/2258780-600x329.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"vi_sao_thu_vien_tieu_hoc_can_phan_mem_quan_ly_chuyen_nghiep\"><\/span>V\u00ec sao th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng b\u1eb1ng s\u1ed5 s\u00e1ch hay b\u1ea3ng t\u00ednh d\u1ec5 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>M\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eadp li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u00e1ch.<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u2013 tr\u1ea3, d\u1ec5 sai s\u00f3t.<\/li>\n<li>Thi\u1ebfu b\u00e1o c\u00e1o th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ecdc sinh kh\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 s\u00e1ch m\u1edbi ho\u1eb7c s\u00e1ch \u0111ang s\u1eb5n c\u00f3.<\/li>\n<li>Vi\u1ec7c tri\u1ec3n khai ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i gi\u00fap t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00f3a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 quy tr\u00ecnh, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 th\u1ee7 th\u01b0 v\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd nhanh ch\u00f3ng, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi m\u1edf ra m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng tra c\u1ee9u tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i cho h\u1ecdc sinh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"oliver_%e2%80%93_phan_mem_quan_ly_thu_vien_thong_minh\"><\/span>Oliver \u2013 Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng minh<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Oliver l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn do Softlink ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea1i h\u01a1n 17.000 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 b\u1eadc ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc, Oliver \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ecdc sinh th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tinh_nang_noi_bat_cua_oliver\"><\/span>T\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Oliver<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3>1. Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u<\/h3>\n<p>Oliver ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng web, cho ph\u00e9p truy c\u1eadp tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb: m\u00e1y t\u00ednh, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh. Giao di\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u00e0m quen v\u00e0 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-16593\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Oliver_Screens-Group-1-1.webp\" alt=\"PH\u1ea6N M\u1ec0M TH\u01af VI\u1ec6N CHO TH\u01af VI\u1ec6N TI\u1ec2U H\u1eccC\n\" width=\"900\" height=\"515\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Oliver_Screens-Group-1-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Oliver_Screens-Group-1-1-699x400.webp 699w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Oliver_Screens-Group-1-1-768x439.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Oliver_Screens-Group-1-1-600x343.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>2. Truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng, kh\u01a1i g\u1ee3i \u0111am m\u00ea \u0111\u1ecdc<\/h3>\n<p>T\u00edch h\u1ee3p t\u00ednh n\u0103ng g\u1ee3i \u00fd s\u00e1ch th\u00f4ng minh, Oliver k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i h\u1ecdc sinh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed1n s\u00e1ch ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1edf th\u00edch, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh th\u00f3i quen \u0111\u1ecdc b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng ngay t\u1eeb b\u1eadc ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<h3>3. Giao di\u1ec7n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i<\/h3>\n<p>Oliver cung c\u1ea5p giao di\u1ec7n d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho h\u1ecdc sinh nh\u1ecf tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh trung h\u1ecdc. Giao di\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u00ednh h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch s\u1ef1 t\u00f2 m\u00f2 v\u00e0 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-16591\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Thumbnail-Blog-student-feedback-helps-development-new-look-oliver-v5-school-library-system-1.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Thumbnail-Blog-student-feedback-helps-development-new-look-oliver-v5-school-library-system-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Thumbnail-Blog-student-feedback-helps-development-new-look-oliver-v5-school-library-system-1-600x400.webp 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Thumbnail-Blog-student-feedback-helps-development-new-look-oliver-v5-school-library-system-1-768x512.webp 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>4. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00f3a th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n<\/h3>\n<p>V\u1edbi giao di\u1ec7n OPAC t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh, th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o phong c\u00e1ch ri\u00eang, qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh, ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<h3>5. Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb<\/h3>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u00f3a c\u00e1c t\u00e1c v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n, gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 th\u01b0 d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n cho vi\u1ec7c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh.<\/p>\n<h3>6. B\u00e1o c\u00e1o, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd<\/h3>\n<p>Oliver cung c\u1ea5p b\u00e1o c\u00e1o d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc ban gi\u00e1m hi\u1ec7u, ph\u1ee5 huynh ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd. Th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng n\u1eafm b\u1eaft t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u2013 tr\u1ea3 v\u00e0 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<h3>7. Tham gia c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u00ean gia th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n Oliver<\/h3>\n<p>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng Oliver to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u, n\u01a1i chia s\u1ebb video h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn, t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<\/p>\n<h3>8. B\u1ea3o m\u1eadt an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 linh ho\u1ea1t<\/h3>\n<p>V\u1eadn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e1m m\u00e2y, Oliver \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o d\u1eef li\u1ec7u th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 truy c\u1eadp m\u1ecdi l\u00fac, m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-16592\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Secure-cloud-Oliver-1.webp\" alt=\"PH\u1ea6N M\u1ec0M TH\u01af VI\u1ec6N CHO TH\u01af VI\u1ec6N TI\u1ec2U H\u1eccC\n\" width=\"900\" height=\"515\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Secure-cloud-Oliver-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Secure-cloud-Oliver-1-699x400.webp 699w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Secure-cloud-Oliver-1-768x439.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Secure-cloud-Oliver-1-600x343.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"loi_ich_cua_oliver_doi_voi_thu_vien_tieu_hoc\"><\/span>L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a Oliver \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3>1. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u0103ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch: Giao di\u1ec7n sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng, g\u1ee3i \u00fd s\u00e1ch theo s\u1edf th\u00edch gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ecdc h\u01a1n.<\/li>\n<li>V\u1edbi giao di\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng web, ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 m\u00e1y t\u00ednh, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh.<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng tra c\u1ee9u th\u00f4ng tin: Oliver gi\u00fap c\u00e1c em l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm, l\u1ecdc th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng quan tr\u1ecdng cho h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp sau n\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>2. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u01b0 &amp; gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd: Quy tr\u00ecnh m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u2013 tr\u1ea3 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, b\u00e1o c\u00e1o th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea nhanh ch\u00f3ng gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng.<\/li>\n<li>D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00f3a d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n: C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ee3i \u00fd t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p t\u1eebng h\u1ecdc sinh, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng danh m\u1ee5c s\u00e1ch cho c\u00e1c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp ho\u1eb7c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 theo d\u00f5i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh: Th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng em m\u01b0\u1ee3n nhi\u1ec1u, m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u00edt, ho\u1eb7c y\u00eau th\u00edch th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng khuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>3. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd kho t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3: Gi\u1ea3m th\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c s\u00e1ch, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u b\u1ed5 sung s\u00e1ch m\u1edbi nh\u1edd s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p xu h\u01b0\u1edbng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1: Oliver \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u s\u1ed1 h\u00f3a d\u1eef li\u1ec7u, v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e1m m\u00e2y, b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt cao v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>M\u1ed9t th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian l\u01b0u tr\u1eef s\u00e1ch, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng. V\u1edbi Oliver, c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd m\u00e0 c\u00f2n n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch cho h\u1ecdc sinh.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-16590 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/post-Phan-mem-thu-vien-cho-thu-vien-tieu-hoc.webp\" alt=\"PH\u1ea6N M\u1ec0M TH\u01af VI\u1ec6N CHO TH\u01af VI\u1ec6N TI\u1ec2U H\u1eccC\n\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/post-Phan-mem-thu-vien-cho-thu-vien-tieu-hoc.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/post-Phan-mem-thu-vien-cho-thu-vien-tieu-hoc-711x400.webp 711w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/post-Phan-mem-thu-vien-cho-thu-vien-tieu-hoc-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/post-Phan-mem-thu-vien-cho-thu-vien-tieu-hoc-600x337.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Oliver \u2013 Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n cho th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc gi\u00fap m\u1edf c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda tri th\u1ee9c, nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch say m\u00ea v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p Oliver v5 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 Trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1, th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i l\u01b0u gi\u1eef s\u00e1ch m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u01a1i g\u1ee3i ni\u1ec1m \u0111am m\u00ea \u0111\u1ecdc v\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 tri th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd chuy\u00ean&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":16590,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-16589","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16589","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=16589"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16589\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":16595,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16589\/revisions\/16595"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16590"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=16589"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=16589"},{"taxonomy"